{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy","slug":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy","title":"Walking the Puppy","title_ko":"강아지 산책","level":"A1","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/cover.webp","summary_ko":"Jun과 Mina가 강아지를 데리고 공원을 산책하며 즐거운 시간을 보냅니다.","wordCount":115,"stage":2,"collection":"daily","pages":[{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Jun has a puppy named Coco.","translation_ko":"준에게는 코코라는 강아지가 있어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Jun","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"has","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":440,"endMs":720},{"word":"a","charStart":8,"charEnd":9,"startMs":720,"endMs":1080},{"word":"puppy","charStart":10,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1100},{"word":"named","charStart":16,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1500},{"word":"Coco","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1840}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"Coco is small and white.","translation_ko":"코코는 작고 하얀 강아지예요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Coco","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":720},{"word":"is","charStart":5,"charEnd":7,"startMs":720,"endMs":880},{"word":"small","charStart":8,"charEnd":13,"startMs":880,"endMs":1180},{"word":"and","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1520},{"word":"white","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1700}]}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"One morning, Jun put on Coco's leash.","translation_ko":"어느 날 아침, 준은 코코에게 목줄을 채웠어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"morning","charStart":4,"charEnd":11,"startMs":280,"endMs":680},{"word":"Jun","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1300},{"word":"put","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1540},{"word":"on","charStart":21,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1820},{"word":"Coco's","charStart":24,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2300},{"word":"leash","charStart":31,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2520}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Let's go to the park!\" he said.","translation_ko":"\"공원에 가자!\" 준이 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Let's","charStart":1,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":500},{"word":"go","charStart":7,"charEnd":9,"startMs":500,"endMs":680},{"word":"to","charStart":10,"charEnd":12,"startMs":680,"endMs":820},{"word":"the","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":820,"endMs":1040},{"word":"park","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1540},{"word":"he","charStart":24,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1720},{"word":"said","charStart":27,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1720,"endMs":1940}]}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"Mina was at the park with her mom.","translation_ko":"미나는 엄마와 함께 공원에 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Mina","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":540},{"word":"was","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":540,"endMs":800},{"word":"at","charStart":9,"charEnd":11,"startMs":800,"endMs":920},{"word":"the","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":920,"endMs":1180},{"word":"park","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1380},{"word":"with","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1700},{"word":"her","charStart":26,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1700,"endMs":1860},{"word":"mom","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2100}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"She saw Jun and ran over.","translation_ko":"미나는 준을 보고 달려왔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"saw","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":460,"endMs":860},{"word":"Jun","charStart":8,"charEnd":11,"startMs":860,"endMs":1220},{"word":"and","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1660},{"word":"ran","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1660,"endMs":1900},{"word":"over","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2160}]}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"Oh, Coco is so cute!\" said Mina.","translation_ko":"\"어머, 코코 정말 귀엽다!\" 미나가 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Oh","charStart":1,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":520},{"word":"Coco","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":740,"endMs":1080},{"word":"is","charStart":10,"charEnd":12,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1360},{"word":"so","charStart":13,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1360,"endMs":1780},{"word":"cute","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1780,"endMs":2520},{"word":"said","charStart":23,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2520,"endMs":2600},{"word":"Mina","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2600,"endMs":2800}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"Coco wagged her tail and jumped up.","translation_ko":"코코는 꼬리를 흔들며 펄쩍 뛰어올랐어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Coco","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":560},{"word":"wagged","charStart":5,"charEnd":11,"startMs":560,"endMs":980},{"word":"her","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":980,"endMs":1140},{"word":"tail","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1440},{"word":"and","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1880},{"word":"jumped","charStart":25,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2060},{"word":"up","charStart":32,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2320}]}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"Jun and Mina walked on the path, and Coco sniffed the flowers.","translation_ko":"준과 미나가 산책로를 걷는 동안 코코는 꽃 냄새를 맡았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Jun","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"and","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":440,"endMs":760},{"word":"Mina","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":760,"endMs":1060},{"word":"walked","charStart":13,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1720},{"word":"on","charStart":20,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1720,"endMs":1940},{"word":"the","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2060},{"word":"path","charStart":27,"charEnd":31,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2400},{"word":"and","charStart":33,"charEnd":36,"startMs":3020,"endMs":3200},{"word":"Coco","charStart":37,"charEnd":41,"startMs":3200,"endMs":3480},{"word":"sniffed","charStart":42,"charEnd":49,"startMs":3480,"endMs":3900},{"word":"the","charStart":50,"charEnd":53,"startMs":3900,"endMs":4120},{"word":"flowers","charStart":54,"charEnd":61,"startMs":4120,"endMs":4440}]}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"Then Coco stopped and pulled the leash hard.","translation_ko":"그러다 코코가 멈추더니 목줄을 세게 당겼어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Then","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":920},{"word":"Coco","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":920,"endMs":1240},{"word":"stopped","charStart":10,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1760},{"word":"and","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2280},{"word":"pulled","charStart":22,"charEnd":28,"startMs":2280,"endMs":2480},{"word":"the","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2480,"endMs":2820},{"word":"leash","charStart":33,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2820,"endMs":2880},{"word":"hard","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2880,"endMs":3260}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"What does she see?\" asked Mina.","translation_ko":"\"뭘 보는 거야?\" 미나가 물었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"What","charStart":1,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"does","charStart":6,"charEnd":10,"startMs":280,"endMs":540},{"word":"she","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":540,"endMs":860},{"word":"see","charStart":15,"charEnd":18,"startMs":860,"endMs":1180},{"word":"asked","charStart":21,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1780,"endMs":1900},{"word":"Mina","charStart":27,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2160}]}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"A small bird was sitting on the bench.","translation_ko":"벤치 위에 작은 새 한 마리가 앉아 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"A","charStart":0,"charEnd":1,"startMs":0,"endMs":200},{"word":"small","charStart":2,"charEnd":7,"startMs":200,"endMs":540},{"word":"bird","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":540,"endMs":860},{"word":"was","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":860,"endMs":1320},{"word":"sitting","charStart":17,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1540},{"word":"on","charStart":25,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1740},{"word":"the","charStart":28,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1740,"endMs":1860},{"word":"bench","charStart":32,"charEnd":37,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2140}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"Coco barked, and the bird flew away.","translation_ko":"코코가 짖자, 새는 날아가 버렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Coco","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"barked","charStart":5,"charEnd":11,"startMs":380,"endMs":940},{"word":"and","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":940,"endMs":1220},{"word":"the","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1460},{"word":"bird","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1620},{"word":"flew","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1940},{"word":"away","charStart":31,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2280}]}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"Jun laughed and Mina laughed too.","translation_ko":"준이 웃었고 미나도 따라 웃었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Jun","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":560},{"word":"laughed","charStart":4,"charEnd":11,"startMs":560,"endMs":1120},{"word":"and","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1580},{"word":"Mina","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1760},{"word":"laughed","charStart":21,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2180},{"word":"too","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2500,"endMs":2540}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Good girl, Coco,\" said Jun.","translation_ko":"\"잘했어, 코코,\" 준이 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Good","charStart":1,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":340},{"word":"girl","charStart":6,"charEnd":10,"startMs":340,"endMs":740},{"word":"Coco","charStart":12,"charEnd":16,"startMs":960,"endMs":1800},{"word":"said","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1800,"endMs":1900},{"word":"Jun","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2200}]}]},{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p9","pageNo":9,"spread":"p9","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/p9.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-p9-s1","ord":0,"text":"They sat on the bench and gave Coco some water.","translation_ko":"두 사람은 벤치에 앉아 코코에게 물을 줬어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-84-walking-the-puppy/audio/p9-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"They","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"sat","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":320,"endMs":600},{"word":"on","charStart":9,"charEnd":11,"startMs":600,"endMs":820},{"word":"the","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":820,"endMs":940},{"word":"bench","charStart":16,"charEnd":21,"startMs":940,"endMs":1220},{"word":"and","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1560},{"word":"gave","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1560,"endMs":1740},{"word":"Coco","charStart":31,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2060},{"word":"some","charStart":36,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2360},{"word":"water","charStart":41,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2360,"endMs":2640}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"강아지의 이름은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["루비","맥스","벨라","코코"],"answerIndex":3,"explain_ko":"준의 강아지 이름은 코코(Coco)예요.","id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"준과 미나는 어디에 갔나요?","type":"mc","options":["학교","도서관","마트","공원"],"answerIndex":3,"explain_ko":"준과 미나는 공원(park)에서 산책을 했어요.","id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"코코가 갑자기 목줄을 당긴 이유는 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["벤치 위의 새를 봐서","물이 마시고 싶어서","집에 가고 싶어서","배가 고파서"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"코코는 벤치에 앉아 있는 작은 새를 보고 목줄을 세게 당겼어요.","id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"코코가 짖자 새는 어떻게 했나요?","type":"mc","options":["날아가 버렸어요","도망쳐 달아났어요","더 크게 울었어요","벤치 아래로 숨었어요"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"코코가 짖자 새는 날아가 버렸어요(the bird flew away).","id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"산책이 끝나고 두 사람은 코코에게 무엇을 주었나요?","type":"mc","options":["물","장난감","과자","간식"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"준과 미나는 벤치에 앉아 코코에게 물(water)을 줬어요.","id":"daily-84-walking-the-puppy-q5","ord":4}]}